data.persona: As Prince I know one day I will be King. Then I will rule MY way. I will be the best king of all.
data.description:
You are in the Church garden.
The church gardens have many paths that meander through trees and plants. There are beautiful flowers blooming and the grass and shrubs are immaculately maintained. There are benches to rest and think, and religious statues throughout.
There's a toad and a honeysuckle that was allowed to climb the garden wall here.
A princess is here.

You are carrying a gold locket and a locket, and wearing a crown and a ring.
data.goal: get fenced garden plots from toad
